---
-       hosts: server
        tasks:
        -       name: sleep
                command: sleep 30 -------------> time taken by command to execute completely
                async: 40 ---------------------> Maximum time (### Time in Seconds ###) 
                poll: 10  ---------------------> After every 10 second it will check for the task status
                
